    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/09/142453215/e8553b2432eb03e295dfe795ef969610_7968382743672291958.png",
                "id": "talent60033",
                "key": "降溫處理",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "降溫處理"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>自身附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">咬咬鯊魚</span>，然後進入<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">夜魂加持</span>，並獲得2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「夜魂值」</span>。（角色進入<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">夜魂加持</span>後不可使用此技能）</p><p>（附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">咬咬鯊魚</span>的角色可以使用特技：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">鯊鯊衝浪板</span>）</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">咬咬鯊魚</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">特技</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雙方切換角色後，且瑪拉妮為出戰角色時：</span>消耗1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「夜魂值」</span>，使敵方出戰角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">啃咬目標</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">特技</span>：鯊鯊衝浪板</p><p>所附屬角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「夜魂值」</span>為0時，棄置此牌；此牌被棄置時，所附屬角色結束<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">夜魂加持</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">夜魂加持</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p>所附屬角色可累積<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「夜魂值」</span>。（最多累積到2點）</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">鯊鯊衝浪板</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">特技</span></p><p>切換到上一個我方角色，使敵方出戰角色附屬1層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">啃咬目標</span>。（若我方後臺角色均被擊倒，則額外消耗1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「夜魂值」</span>）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/09/142453215/6eca0515aa0b943ce4863f23e7bac54f_1344696648183141170.png",
                "id": "talent68168",
                "key": "踏鯊破浪",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "踏鯊破浪"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">鯊鯊飛彈</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">鯊鯊飛彈</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span>（可疊加，沒有上限）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/09/142453215/de980cad3d9422986776632fa61c2eff_8013747312013735503.png",
                "id": "talent37489",
                "key": "爆瀑飛彈",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "爆瀑飛彈"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">特技</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雙方切換角色後，且瑪拉妮為出戰角色時：</span>消耗1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「夜魂值」</span>，使敵方出戰角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">啃咬目標</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">特技</span>：鯊鯊衝浪板</p><p>所附屬角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「夜魂值」</span>為0時，棄置此牌；此牌被棄置時，所附屬角色結束<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">夜魂加持</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/09/142453215/34858f53e503048f7850eb3a18565223_1205579496471342954.png",
                "id": "talent28247",
                "key": "咬咬鯊魚",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/09/142453215/6fc92bf55b26c115eefe4f2a113677e0_4044916185983437337.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "咬咬鯊魚"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span>（可疊加，沒有上限）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/09/142453215/34858f53e503048f7850eb3a18565223_1515959138790069478.png",
                "id": "talent30129",
                "key": "鯊鯊飛彈",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/09/142453215/f2ea88f3013a7c33fb47942114373377_6203072891076417868.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "鯊鯊飛彈"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著水元素，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到物理或火元素傷害後提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次火元素或雷元素傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[草原核]</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/09/142453215/a397858dcc595566da0714d3291bca3a_4446148379037675196.png",
                "id": "talent82063",
                "key": "水元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "水元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">啃咬目標</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">受到瑪拉妮或鯊鯊飛彈傷害時：</span>移除此效果，每層使此傷害+2。</p><p>（層數可疊加，沒有上限）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">特技</span></strong></p><p>出戰角色裝備有「特技」卡牌時，就可以使用對應的「特技」。</p><p>使用「特技」是一種「戰鬥行動」。角色因凍結、石化、眩暈等原因無法使用技能時，也會同時無法使用「特技」。</p><p>角色使用「特技」時不視為使用技能，無法觸發「使用技能後」、「角色引發元素反應後」等效果；角色使用「特技」造成的傷害不視為角色造成的傷害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/09/142453215/549098b1d2703a18c54be7721e6b85e4_1726856854870116113.png",
